Interface FloatIndexedContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FloatCollection, FloatContainer, java.lang.Iterable<FloatCursor>, java.util.RandomAccess
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    @Generated(date="2020-06-01T10:41:25+0200",
           value="KTypeIndexedContainer.java")
public interface FloatIndexedContainer
extends FloatCollection, java.util.RandomAccess
    An indexed container provides random access to elements based on an index. Indexes are zero-based.
